{"tid":2445072,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夜場打滾十年 　酒吧老闆娘論蘭桂坊百態︰女生躺在斜路 　洋人上下其手","createTime":"2021-03-13T10:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T18:11:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d5450af09f3903216efd35f1f4e7adb16c995fa6","tid":2445072,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8BUd-JiwJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL8BUd-JiwJQ&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=3eb5027b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8BUd-JiwJQ</a><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n十年，從懵懂至成熟，從思想到生理，一一在你我身上留下痕跡。這段歲月，她選擇奉上青春在酒吧業打拼；時至今日，她早已見盡夜蒲糜爛百態，臉上甜美笑容卻依舊。<br />\n<br />\n舞曲轟炸，場內一對對紅塵男女四目交投，迸出火花──Save Bar的90後老闆娘Giann對這些畫面卻早已麻木，「見得太多了」，她淡淡說。<br />\n<br />\n這些日子大家常在街頭撿到催淚彈殼，那些年Giann在工作的蘭桂坊亦見盡「執屍」情景。她憶述，凌晨下班時，沿路常見爛醉女子躺地，身上財物空空如也，在旁有洋人撩撥試探是否仍清醒。Giann每每多走兩步，向附近巡警報案，以免醉娃入虎口。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_714347_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_714347_0&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=64d28ec8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_714347_0&h=e3f14faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_714347_0</a>"},{"pid":"269dbbbbbfdc11129e616534a69e22d9d78cd050","tid":2445072,"uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":10,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這些日子大家常在街頭撿到催淚彈殼，那些年Giann在工作的蘭桂坊亦見盡「執屍」情景。她憶述，凌晨下班時，沿路常見爛醉女子躺地，身上財物空空如也，在旁有洋人撩撥試探是否仍清醒。Giann每每多走兩步，向附近巡警報案，以免醉娃入虎口。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD女去得, 就自己預咗架啦"},{"pid":"9b8877096fab844c89ecde6ef0b162e0b9eeec0f","tid":2445072,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"支持港府禁鬼佬入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541811e971de71